des:
After connecting Alexa to your Kian Smart products in a few simple steps:
(1). Download Kian Smart from Android or ios app store;
(two). Register an account on our app;
(3). You need to have some Kian Smart devices;
(4). Configure these devices in our app and change the appropriate name for your devices that will be used in the Skill;
(5). Download Amazon app “Alexa” from Android, ios or Amazon app;
(6). Configure the Echo with the “Alexa” app;
(7). Search for the Skill in the Skills category of the “Alexa” application;
(8). Click Activate Skill and you will be redirected to the Kian Smart login page;
(9).Open "Kian Smart" app, click More service, choose "Alexa". Link with verification code, copy the code, put the code on the login page；
(10). Now all the setup is complete. You can enjoy voice control on your home devices like these:
“Alexa, turn on the bedroom light.”
“Alexa, turn off the bedroom light.”
“Alexa, adjust bedroom light brightness to 50 percent.”
“Alexa, increase bedroom brightness.”
“Alexa, dim the bedroom light by 50.”
“Alexa, change the bedroom light to green.”
“Alexa, turn bedroom lights cooler.”
